  <h2>Why Everything You've Tried<br><span>Has Failed You</span></h2>
  <div class="s2-divider"></div>

  <p>I want to be clear about something. The eye creams you've tried — CeraVe, The Ordinary, La Roche-Posay, RoC — are not bad products. They're made by serious companies with real scientists. But they have one fundamental problem that no amount of marketing budget can fix.</p>

  <!-- IMAGE ÉTAGÈRE CRÈMES -->
