  <div class="s2-science">
    <p><strong>The problem was never the ingredients.</strong> It was always the delivery. Without a mechanism to breach the skin barrier and carry actives into the dermis, no topical product can reach the source of dark circles. This is basic biology — not a brand failure.</p>
  </div>

