      <h3>The "Cold Spoon" Trap</h3>
      <p>Millions of men do this every morning. And it works — for exactly 20 minutes.</p>
      <p>Cold temporarily constricts vessels. But the moment skin returns to body temperature, every symptom comes back. You haven't treated anything. You've just delayed it by half an hour.</p>
      <p><strong>This is not a solution. This is a coping mechanism.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

