      <div class="s3-step-content">
        <strong>750 micro-channels open in the dermis</strong>
        <p>The moment you press Liftora against your skin, 750 ultra-fine needles made of dissolving hyaluronic acid penetrate precisely 0.3–0.5mm into the dermis. Each needle is thinner than a human hair. You feel absolutely nothing. These channels stay open for approximately 2 hours — creating a direct delivery route into the exact layer where dark circles originate.</p>
