        <p>Through these open channels, Liftora's formula is delivered exactly where it needs to go — not onto the surface, not into the epidermis, but directly into the dermis. This is a 10x improvement in bioavailability compared to any topical cream. The actives don't have to fight through the skin barrier because they have a direct path straight to the source.</p>
