        <p>Caffeine constricts blood vessels and drains fluid pooling (cause #3). Vitamin C breaks down oxidized hemoglobin and reduces dark pigmentation (cause #1). Peptides + Hyaluronic Acid stimulate collagen production and plump thinning tissue (cause #2). Ceramides seal the barrier and lock in results long-term. All 5 working simultaneously at the right depth.</p>
        <span class="s3-step-badge">All 3 root causes addressed at once</span>
      </div>
