        <p>The needles are made of 100% dissolvable hyaluronic acid. Within 2 hours, they dissolve entirely inside the skin — becoming an additional dose of hydrating HA delivered directly into the dermis. No extraction needed, no redness, no clinic visit. Simply remove the patch in the morning and discard it.</p>
