  <h3>The 5-Ingredient Formula — What Each One Does</h3>
  <p>Every ingredient in Liftora was selected for one reason: clinical evidence of effectiveness for under-eye dark circles, when delivered at the right depth. Combined with microneedle delivery, these become exponentially more effective than in any cream.</p>

  <div class="s3-img-full">
