      <div class="s4-faq-a">
        <p>Not at all. The micro-needles are 0.3–0.5mm long and thinner than a human hair. Most users describe the sensation as a very slight tingling at most — many feel nothing at all. The needles are made of dissolving hyaluronic acid, not metal. There is no redness, no irritation, and no recovery time.</p>
